title: #225: Vagina Turkey Baster (@RachelJSimmons)
itunes:title: Vagina Turkey Baster with Rachel J. Simmons
description: Rachel Simmons and I had a high school reunion for two last week. And while we were doing that, we recorded a podcast about artificial insemination. A few years ago, Rachel got knocked up the modern way, by paying for sperm to be stuffed inside her by a medical professional. I had some questions. This was a fun talk with two people who have known each other for almost 25 years.
